Gospel star Lundi Tyamara passed away early hours this morning.&nbsp; The 38-year-old had been fighting for his life at Edenvale Hospital in Ekurhuleni since the festive season. READ: LUNDI'S STILL FIGHTING!&nbsp; Lundi was treated for stomach TB and a liver condition. Throughout the week many South Africans came together to pray for Lundi.&nbsp; READ: MZANSI PRAYS FOR SICK LUNDI More details to follow.&nbsp;